{"type":"message","id":"dec4928a","parentId":"2dcd3889","timestamp":"2026-06-25T08:06:57.502Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-8fa0d687f6e54b8ba1322a842a5ea1be","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def goto_home_verify_stability(self) -> dict[str, Any]:\r\n        \"\"\"P6.1: 设置预置点10为HOME位，验证稳定性。\r\n\r\n        M1_method.csv 要求: \"验证持续20点/2s位置0误差\"\r\n        即: 连续20点采样，每点 pan/tilt/zoom 必须 严格等于 HOME_COORDS\r\n\r\n        步骤:\r\n        1. 直接设置预置点10为 HOME_COORDS (1800, 450, 10)\r\n        2. 移动到预置点10\r\n        3. 验证稳定性: 连续20点采样，每点严格等于 HOME_COORDS\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        result = {\r\n            \"success\": False,\r\n            \"home_preset\": DEFAULT_PTZ_PRESET,\r\n            \"stability_check\": False,\r\n            \"readings\": [],\r\n            \"preset_set\": False,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        # Step 1: 直接设置预置点10为 HOME_COORDS (覆盖)\r\n        LOG.log(\"info\", \"设置预置点10为 HOME 坐标 (1800, 450, 10)\")\r\n        preset_success = self.ptz.set_preset(\r\n            preset_id=DEFAULT_PTZ_PRESET,\r\n            pan=HOME_COORDS[\"pan\"],\r\n            tilt=HOME_COORDS[\"tilt\"],\r\n            zoom=HOME_COORDS[\"zoom\"],\r\n            name=\"HOME\"\r\n        )\r\n        if not preset_success:\r\n            result[\"error\"] = \"设置预置点10失败\"\r\n\n[789 more lines in file. Use offset=192 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782374817502}}
{"type":"message","id":"0099513a","parentId":"dec4928a","timestamp":"2026-06-25T08:06:57.502Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-dff10ac75b3b4706b397aaf0f5336244","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n        步骤:\r\n        1. gotohome 回到零位，稳定STABILIZATION_SECONDS\r\n        2. 正向 PAN=+50 连续移动，实时监测跳变/稳定，立刻停止\r\n        3. 稳定1秒\r\n        4. 反向 PAN=-50 连续移动，实时监测跳变/稳定，立刻停止\r\n        5. 回到HOME位，稳定1秒\r\n        6. 构建结果返回\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        result = {\r\n            \"success\": False,\r\n            \"pan_min\": self.PAN_MIN,\r\n            \"pan_max\": self.PAN_MAX,\r\n            \"crossing_detected\": False,\r\n            \"is_infinite\": False,\r\n            \"readings\": [],\r\n            \"error\": None,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        # 步骤1: 回到 HOME 位作为起点，稳定\r\n        if not self.ptz.goto_home():\r\n            result[\"error\"] = \"回到HOME失败\"\r\n            return result\r\n\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\r\n        pan_positive_infinite = False\r\n        pan_negative_infinite = False\r\n        pan_max_val = self.PAN_MAX  # default if infinite\r\n        pan_min_val = self.PAN_MIN  # default if infinite\r\n\r\n        # 步骤2: 正向 PAN=+50 连续移动监测\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(pan=50, tilt=0, zoom=0)\r\n        last_pan = None\r\n        same_pan_count = 0\r\n\n[666 more lines in file. Use offset=315 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782374817502}}
{"type":"message","id":"030f7bea","parentId":"0099513a","timestamp":"2026-06-25T08:06:57.502Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-4e386f58cd2e443e86031588b26eec73","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            self.ptz.continuous_move(0, 0, 0)\r\n            result[\"readings\"].append({\r\n                \"timeout\": True, \"pan\": current_pan, \"direction\": \"positive\"\r\n            })\r\n\r\n        # 正向已判定无限位，直接返回结果，不测反向\r\n        if pan_positive_infinite:\r\n            self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n            time.sleep(1)\r\n            result[\"pan_min\"] = self.PAN_MIN\r\n            result[\"pan_max\"] = self.PAN_MAX\r\n            result[\"is_infinite\"] = True\r\n            result[\"crossing_detected\"] = True\r\n            result[\"readings\"].append({\"conclusion\": \"无限位（正向检测到跳变）\"})\r\n            result[\"success\"] = True\r\n            return result\r\n\r\n        # 步骤3: 稳定\r\n        time.sleep(1)\r\n\r\n        # 步骤4: 反向 PAN=-50 连续移动监测（仅当正向未判定无限位时执行）\r\n        same_pan_count = 0\r\n        last_pan = None\r\n        start_time = time.time()\r\n        negative_exited = False\r\n\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(pan=-50, tilt=0, zoom=0)\r\n\r\n        while not negative_exited and (time.time() - start_time) < 30.0:\r\n            pos = self._get_position()\r\n            current_pan = pos.get(\"pan\", 0)\r\n            self._write_csv_row(current_pan, pos.get(\"tilt\", 0), pos.get(\"zoom\", 0))\r\n            result[\"readings\"].append({\r\n                \"pan\": current_pan,\r\n                \"direction\": \"negative\",\r\n                \"same_count\": same_pan_count,\r\n            })\r\n\r\n            if last_pan is not None:\r\n                # JUMP CHECK: delta > 1800\r\n\n[571 more lines in file. Use offset=410 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782374817502}}
