{"type":"message","id":"63089287","parentId":"64425fc2","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:16:31.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板问是否完成了。我之前被中断了，需要继续完成任务。\n\n任务是：修改 gotohome 之后稳定的逻辑\n- 不是分开：gotohome + 单独稳定\n- 改成：gotohome + 等待 PTZ 数值等于 HOME (1800, 450, 10)\n- 等待 20 点（2秒）\n- 误差 = 0\n- 去掉 gotohome 单独稳定的设计\n\n我还没有执行修改。现在需要：\n1. 在 ptz.py 中添加 `goto_home_and_wait()` 方法\n2. 在 limit.py 中替换所有 `goto_home()` + `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)` 的地方\n\n让我立即执行修改。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"还没完成，继续执行。\n\n**修改步骤**：\n1. ptz.py 添加 `goto_home_and_wait()` 方法\n2. limit.py 替换所有 gotohome + 稳定逻辑"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-56fe3d2609ee4e7aad7b7f5983436fc2","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\ptz\\isapi\\ptz.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    def goto_home(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"Move to HOME preset 10.\"\"\"\n        if not self.goto_preset(self.home_preset):\n            LOG.log(\"error\", \"goto_home: failed to goto preset\")\n            return False\n        LOG.log(\"done\", \"goto_home: preset 10 sent\")\n        return True","newText":"    def goto_home(self) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"Move to HOME preset 10.\"\"\"\n        if not self.goto_preset(self.home_preset):\n            LOG.log(\"error\", \"goto_home: failed to goto preset\")\n            return False\n        LOG.log(\"done\", \"goto_home: preset 10 sent\")\n        return True\n\n    def goto_home_and_wait(self, samples: int = 20, interval: float = 0.1, max_wait: float = 30.0) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"goto_home 并等待位置等于 HOME_COORDS (1800, 450, 10)。\n\n        步骤:\n        1. goto_home() 移动到预置点10\n        2. 循环采样，等待连续 samples 点等于 HOME_COORDS\n        3. 误差 = 0（严格相等）\n\n        Args:\n            samples: 连续稳定采样数 (default: 20)\n            interval: 采样间隔 (default: 0.1s)\n            max_wait: 最大等待时间 (default: 30s)\n\n        Returns:\n            True = 到达 HOME 并稳定\n            False = 超时失败\n        \"\"\"\n        # 发送 goto_home\n        if not self.goto_home():\n            LOG.log(\"error\", \"goto_home_and_wait: goto_home failed\")\n            return False\n\n        # 等待位置等于 HOME_COORDS\n        start_time = time.time()\n        stable_count = 0\n        target = {\"pan\": 1800, \"tilt\": 450, \"zoom\": 10}\n\n        while time.time() - start_time < max_wait:\n            pos = self.get_position()\n            if not pos:\n                time.sleep(interval)\n                continue\n\n            # 严格相等检查\n            if (pos.get(\"pan\") == target[\"pan\"] and\n                pos.get(\"tilt\") == target[\"tilt\"] and\n                pos.get(\"zoom\") == target[\"zoom\"]):\n                stable_count += 1\n                if stable_count >= samples:\n                    LOG.log(\"done\", f\"goto_home_and_wait: 到达 HOME 并稳定 ({samples}点)\")\n                    return True\n            else:\n                stable_count = 0\n\n            time.sleep(interval)\n\n        LOG.log(\"warning\", f\"goto_home_and_wait: 超时，最终位置 {pos}\")\n        return False"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":36550,"output":880,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782382546112,"responseId":"cht000d3607@dx19efe475ad1ba5e452"}}
