{"type":"message","id":"4cd53b02","parentId":"2222307c","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:17:11.252Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-ce9df62ff72540cdb7ac804bb36ecad8","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            \"readings\": [],\r\n            \"error\": None,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        # 步骤1: 回到 HOME 位作为起点，稳定\r\n        if not self.ptz.goto_home():\r\n            result[\"error\"] = \"回到HOME失败\"\r\n            return result\r\n\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\r\n        pan_positive_infinite = False\r\n        pan_negative_infinite = False\r\n        pan_max_val = self.PAN_MAX  # default if infinite\r\n        pan_min_val = self.PAN_MIN  # default if infinite\r\n\r\n        # 步骤2: 正向 PAN=+50 连续移动监测\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(pan=50, tilt=0, zoom=0)\r\n        last_pan = None\r\n        same_pan_count = 0\r\n        start_time = time.time()\r\n        positive_exited = False\r\n        first_pan = None\r\n        pan_increasing = None  # 方向判断\r\n\r\n        while not positive_exited and (time.time() - start_time) < 30.0:\r\n            pos = self._get_position()\r\n            current_pan = pos.get(\"pan\", 0)\r\n            self._write_csv_row(current_pan, pos.get(\"tilt\", 0), pos.get(\"zoom\", 0))\r\n            result[\"readings\"].append({\r\n\n[656 more lines in file. Use offset=325 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782382631252}}
{"type":"message","id":"7740f49f","parentId":"4cd53b02","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:17:11.252Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-696c00573aa4460a82164f5cebefac28","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            \"flip_detected_at\": None,\r\n            \"readings\": [],\r\n            \"error\": None,\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        # 步骤1: 回到 HOME 位，稳定\r\n        if not self.ptz.goto_home():\r\n            result[\"error\"] = \"回到HOME失败\"\r\n            return result\r\n\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\r\n        # 步骤2: 正向 Tilt=+50 上移\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(pan=0, tilt=50, zoom=0)\r\n        flipped = False\r\n        peak_tilt = 0.0\r\n        readings_up = []\r\n        same_tilt_count = 0\r\n        last_tilt = None\r\n        tilt_stopped = False\r\n        start = time.time()\r\n        first_tilt = None\r\n        tilt_increasing = None  # 方向判断\r\n\r\n        while not tilt_stopped and (time.time() - start) < 60.0:\r\n            time.sleep(SAMPLE_INTERVAL)\r\n            pos = self._get_position()\r\n            t = pos.get(\"tilt\", 0)\r\n            self._write_csv_row(pos.get(\"pan\", 0), t, pos.get(\"zoom\", 0))\r\n            readings_up.append(t)\r\n\n[461 more lines in file. Use offset=520 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782382631252}}
{"type":"message","id":"809b6444","parentId":"7740f49f","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:17:11.252Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-30f21f3231bd4a1198e1e15acfe0b49f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        # 回到 HOME 位\r\n        if not self.ptz.goto_home():\r\n            result[\"error\"] = \"回到HOME失败\"\r\n            return result\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\r\n        # Zoom+ 方向: Z=+50（使用 PTZController 的 zoom_in 接口）\r\n        home_pos = self._get_position()\r\n        home_zoom = home_pos.get(\"zoom\", 0)\r\n        result[\"readings\"].append({\"direction\": \"home\", \"zoom\": home_zoom})\r\n\r\n        # Zoom In 方向\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=50)\r\n        zoom_in_start = time.time()\r\n        last_zoom_val = home_zoom\r\n        last_change_time = zoom_in_start\r\n        max_zoom_observed = home_zoom\r\n\r\n        start = time.time()\r\n        while time.time() - start < 30:  # 最多30s超时保护\r\n            time.sleep(0.1)\r\n            pos = self._get_position()\r\n            z = pos.get(\"zoom\", 0)\r\n            self._write_csv_row(pos.get(\"pan\", 0), pos.get(\"tilt\", 0), z)\r\n            result[\"readings\"].append({\"direction\": \"zoom_in\", \"zoom\": z})\r\n            if z != last_zoom_val:\r\n                last_zoom_val = z\r\n                last_change_time = time.time()\r\n                max_zoom_observed = max(max_zoom_observed, z)\r\n            if time.time() - last_change_time >= self.ZOOM_STABLE_SECONDS:\r\n                LOG.log('done', 'Zoom入限位已稳定2s')\r\n                break\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(0, 0, 0)\r\n        time.sleep(1)\r\n\r\n        result[\"zoom_max_observed\"] = max_zoom_observed\r\n\r\n        # 回到 HOME 位\r\n        self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\n[286 more lines in file. Use offset=695 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782382631252}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d0fecfc","parentId":"809b6444","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:17:11.252Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-08caab63cfce49e1b7b120e1668824a2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        time.sleep(1)\r\n\r\n        result[\"zoom_max_observed\"] = max_zoom_observed\r\n\r\n        # 回到 HOME 位\r\n        self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\r\n        # Zoom Out 方向: Z=-50 (从 HOME 位开始)\r\n        home_pos = self._get_position()\r\n        home_zoom = home_pos.get(\"zoom\", 0)\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(pan=0, tilt=0, zoom=-50)\r\n        last_zoom_val = home_zoom\r\n        last_change_time = time.time()\r\n        min_zoom_observed = home_zoom\r\n\r\n        start = time.time()\r\n        while time.time() - start < 30:\r\n            time.sleep(0.1)\r\n            pos = self._get_position()\r\n            z = pos.get(\"zoom\", 0)\r\n            self._write_csv_row(pos.get(\"pan\", 0), pos.get(\"tilt\", 0), z)\r\n            result[\"readings\"].append({\"direction\": \"zoom_out\", \"zoom\": z})\r\n            if z != last_zoom_val:\r\n                last_zoom_val = z\r\n                last_change_time = time.time()\r\n                min_zoom_observed = min(min_zoom_observed, z)\r\n            if time.time() - last_change_time >= self.ZOOM_STABLE_SECONDS:\r\n                LOG.log('done', 'Zoom出限位已稳定2s')\r\n                break\r\n        self.ptz.continuous_move(0, 0, 0)\r\n        time.sleep(1)\r\n\r\n        # 回到 HOME\r\n        self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\r\n        result[\"zoom_min_observed\"] = min_zoom_observed\r\n        # P6.5: ZOOM_MAX=320, ZOOM_MIN=10 per M1_method.csv 测试阶段标准\r\n        result[\"zoom_min\"] = int(min_zoom_observed) if min_zoom_observed is not None else self.ZOOM_MIN\r\n\n[253 more lines in file. Use offset=728 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782382631252}}
{"type":"message","id":"92a5a511","parentId":"4d0fecfc","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:17:11.253Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-ceaa54ca97be426e931d62626e29d885","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        self.ptz.continuous_move(0, 0, 0)\r\n        time.sleep(1)\r\n\r\n        # 回到 HOME\r\n        self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\r\n\r\n        result[\"zoom_min_observed\"] = min_zoom_observed\r\n        # P6.5: ZOOM_MAX=320, ZOOM_MIN=10 per M1_method.csv 测试阶段标准\r\n        result[\"zoom_min\"] = int(min_zoom_observed) if min_zoom_observed is not None else self.ZOOM_MIN\r\n        result[\"zoom_max\"] = int(max_zoom_observed) if max_zoom_observed is not None else self.ZOOM_MAX\r\n\r\n        self._zoom_limits[\"min\"] = self.ZOOM_MIN if min_zoom_observed is None else int(min_zoom_observed)\r\n        self._zoom_limits[\"max\"] = self.ZOOM_MAX if max_zoom_observed is None else int(max_zoom_observed)\r\n\r\n        result[\"success\"] = True\r\n\r\n        return result\r\n\r\n    # --- P6.6: 设备还原 ---\r\n\r\n    def restore_device(self) -> bool:\r\n        \"\"\"P6.6: 设备还原 - 恢复默认参数，回到HOME位。\"\"\"\r\n        try:\r\n            restore_xml = '<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>'\r\n            restore_xml += '<restore xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\"/>'\r\n            restore_result = self.client.put(\"/System/restoreDefaults\", restore_xml)\r\n            if restore_result.status_code == 200:\r\n                LOG.log('done', '设备参数已恢复默认')\r\n            else:\r\n                LOG.log('warning', '设备还原API返回 %d' % restore_result.status_code)\r\n        except Exception as e:\r\n            LOG.log('warning', '设备还原异常: %s' % e)\r\n\r\n        # 回到 HOME 位\r\n        return self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n\r\n    # --- 完整测试流程 ---\r\n\r\n    def run_all_tests(self, progress_callback=None) -> dict[str, Any]:\r\n\n[223 more lines in file. Use offset=758 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782382631252}}
{"type":"message","id":"332b821a","parentId":"92a5a511","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:17:11.254Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-e57b14b7215749f7b537c3e85fc41fc1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\n        # P6.6: 设备还原\r\n        restore_ok = self.restore_device()\r\n\r\n        # 回到 HOME（重试确保成功）\r\n        home_ok = self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n        if not home_ok:\r\n            LOG.log('warning', 'limit 测试结束 goto_home 失败，重试')\r\n            self.ptz.continuous_move(0, 0, 0)\r\n            time.sleep(2)\r\n            home_ok = self.ptz.goto_home()\r\n        time.sleep(1)\r\n        if home_ok:\r\n            LOG.log('done', 'limit 测试完成，设备已回到 HOME 位')\r\n        else:\r\n            LOG.log('error', 'limit 测试完成，回到 HOME 位失败')\r\n\r\n        # 构造方向信息\r\n        direction_info = {\r\n            \"pan\": {\"positive_command_increases\": pan_limits.get(\"positive_command_increases\")},\r\n            \"tilt\": {\"positive_command_increases\": tilt_limits.get(\"positive_command_increases\")},\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        result = {\r\n            \"success\": True,\r\n            \"pan_min\": pan_limits.get(\"pan_min\", self.PAN_MIN),\r\n            \"pan_max\": pan_limits.get(\"pan_max\", self.PAN_MAX),\r\n            \"pan_has_limit\": not pan_limits.get(\"is_infinite\", False),\r\n            \"is_infinite\": pan_limits.get(\"is_infinite\", False),\r\n            \"tilt_min\": tilt_limits.get(\"tilt_min\", self.TILT_MIN),\r\n            \"tilt_max\": tilt_limits.get(\"tilt_max\", self.TILT_MAX),\r\n            \"zoom_min\": zoom_limits.get(\"zoom_min\", self.ZOOM_MIN),\r\n            \"zoom_max\": zoom_limits.get(\"zoom_max\", self.ZOOM_MAX),\r\n            \"has_flip\": tilt_limits.get(\"has_flip\", False),\r\n            \"stability_check\": stability.get(\"stability_check\", False),\r\n            \"mac_info\": mac_info,\r\n            \"direction_info\": direction_info,\r\n            \"csv_path\": self._csv_path,\r\n            \"restore_ok\": restore_ok,\r\n        }\r\n\n[133 more lines in file. Use offset=848 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782382631252}}
{"type":"message","id":"577cbed3","parentId":"332b821a","timestamp":"2026-06-25T10:17:31.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture of all the locations that need to be changed. Let me also check line 377 and 446 to see what goto_home calls look like there.\n\nLet me also check the goto_home_verify_stability method more carefully (line 204 area) since it's the dedicated P6.1 test.\n\nLet me now plan the exact edits:\n\n1. **test_pan_limits** (line 300-304): \n   - `if not self.ptz.goto_home()` → `if not self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n   - Remove `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)`\n\n2. **test_pan_limits** (line 377):\n   - `self.ptz.goto_home()` → `self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()` \n   - Remove `time.sleep(1)` after it (but wait, it's followed by `time.sleep(1)` not `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)`)\n\n3. **test_pan_limits** (line 446):\n   - `self.ptz.goto_home()` - need to check context\n\n4. **test_tilt_limits** (line 496-500):\n   - `if not self.ptz.goto_home()` → `if not self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n   - Remove `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)`\n\n5. **test_tilt_limits** (line 630):\n   - `if not self.ptz.goto_home()` → need to check context\n\n6. **test_zoom_limits** (line 656-659):\n   - `if not self.ptz.goto_home()` → `if not self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n   - Remove `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)`\n\n7. **test_zoom_limits** (line 693-694):\n   - `self.ptz.goto_home()` → `self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n   - Remove `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)`\n\n8. **test_zoom_limits** (line 722-723):\n   - `self.ptz.goto_home()` → `self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n   - Remove `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)`\n\n9. **restore_device** (line 753):\n   - `return self.ptz.goto_home()` → `return self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n\n10. **run_all_tests** (line 813-818):\n    - `home_ok = self.ptz.goto_home()` → `home_ok = self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n    - Remove `time.sleep(1)` after it\n    - The retry logic: `home_ok = self.ptz.goto_home()` → `home_ok = self.ptz.goto_home_and_wait()`\n\nLet me also check the P6.1 goto_home_verify_stability method (line 192-228). The current implementation:\n- Step 1: set_preset(10, 1800, 450, 10, \"HOME\")\n- Step 2: goto_preset(10)\n- Step 3: time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\n- Step 4: sample 20 points, check each equals HOME_COORDS\n\nThe new behavior should be:\n- After gotohome, wait for position to equal HOME_COORDS for 20 points\n- No separate time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\n\nBut wait - P6.1's purpose is both to set the preset and verify stability. The set_preset is a separate operation from goto_home. Let me re-read that method carefully.\n\nActually, looking at P6.1 method:\n1. It sets preset 10 to HOME_COORDS (line 182-189)\n2. It calls goto_preset(10) (line 193-194) - NOT goto_home()\n3. time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS) (line 204)\n4. Samples 20 points checking equal to HOME_COORDS (line 208-227)\n\nSo P6.1's gotohome uses `self.ptz.goto_preset(10)` directly, not `self.ptz.goto_home()`. But the logic should be the same: after goto_preset(10), wait for position to equal HOME_COORDS. I need to replace the time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS) with a loop that waits for the position to match HOME_COORDS for 20 points.\n\nLet me read the full P6.1 method to see the complete context:\n\nFrom what I've already read, line 192-230:\n```python\n        # Step 2: 移动到预置点10\n        LOG.log(\"info\", \"移动到预置点10\")\n        goto_success = self.ptz.goto_preset(DEFAULT_PTZ_PRESET)\n        if not goto_success:\n            result[\"error\"] = \"移动到预置点10失败\"\n            return result\n\n        time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)\n\n        # Step 3: 持续采样 20 点 @ 0.1s，验证每点严格等于 HOME_COORDS\n        readings = []\n        expected = HOME_COORDS  # {\"pan\": 1800, \"tilt\": 450, \"zoom\": 10}\n        all_match = True\n```\n\nI should replace the time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS) with a loop, but that's essentially the same as what follows. Let me think about this more carefully.\n\nThe current P6.1 code:\n1. goto_preset(10)\n2. time.sleep(2)  -- just a blind wait\n3. Then sample 20 points at 0.1s interval checking if each == HOME_COORDS\n\nThe intent of the fix is: instead of blind wait (time.sleep), actively check that position == HOME_COORDS for 20 consecutive points.\n\nActually, the simplest approach for P6.1 would be to use `goto_home_and_wait()` instead of `goto_preset(10)` + `time.sleep(STABILIZATION_SECONDS)`. But the method also needs to set_preset first.\n\nLet me re-think: the P6.1 method does:\n1. SET preset 10 (to make sure it's correct)\n2. GO TO preset 10\n3. Wait for stability\n\nI can simplify step 2+3 into goto_home_and_wait(). Let me do that.\n\nNow let me also check what happens on lines 377 and 446:","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"让我也看下 line 377 和 446 的上下文：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2bfcefc19aa64692a6ffd4e9","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":15,"offset":370,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\limit.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fcc1a5380d534f3a85fa4798","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":15,"offset":440,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\limit.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b84a32bf26534284a5a7bf07","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":15,"offset":620,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\advanced\\limit.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":44500,"output":1736,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46236,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782382631253,"responseId":"cht000d23ab@dx19efe489eb9b893752"}}
